OpenFlow.NBAPI
Interface ControllerContext.InternalExtension

Enclosing class:
ControllerContext
public static interface ControllerContext.InternalExtension

Internal extension message handlers.

Implementation note: These extension handlers are generally expected to be invoked from within the client's reader thread, and should therefore be designed to impose minimal delays when the call-back methods are invoked.
